                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6571" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0457</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8587 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薪酬体系改革：济南二机床的共富中国梦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Compensation system reform: JIER&#39;s Chinese dream of common prosperity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘冰，曲宵慧，白明磊，李岳泽，刘光建</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">济南二机床集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">济南二机床；薪酬体系改革；全面薪酬；共同富裕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">JIER；Compensation System Reform; Total Rewards; Common Prosperity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为一家拥有八十多年发展历史的国有企业，济南二机床的高质量发展离不开员工的潜心主业和开拓创新。面对日益激烈的市场竞争，传统的薪酬体系难以适应企业发展的要求,身处完全竞争性行业的济二需要进一步激发员工的积极性、主动性和创造性。因此，如何全方位满足员工需要、最大化薪酬激励效果成为济二亟待解决的关键问题。本案例描述了济二进行薪酬改革的背景、具体实施以及取得的成效，全面展示了济二薪酬体系改革的过程。通过对本案例的分析和讨论，可以系统地深化学生对于进行薪酬体系变革的原因、薪酬体系设计所需遵循的原则、全面薪酬的内涵以及全面薪酬推进共同富裕的实现路径四个问题的认识和理解，并为其他企业开展薪酬体系变革、推进共同富裕提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a state-owned enterprise with more than 80 years, the high-quality development of JIER is inseparable from the employees&#39; dedication to the main business and innovation. Facing the increasingly fierce market competition, JIER, who is in a completely competitive industry, needs to further stimulate the enthusiasm, initiative and creativity of employees. The traditional compensation system has been difficult to adapt to the development of enterprise in the new era. Therefore, how to fully meet the needs of employees and maximize the effect of compensation incentives has become a key issue to be solved urgently. This case describes the background, implementation and achievements of the compensation reform in JIER, comprehensively showing the reform process. Through the analysis and discussion of this case, students can systematically deepen their understanding of the reasons for the compensation system reform, the principles of compensation system design, the connotation of total rewards and the realization path of total rewards to promote common prosperity. These questions can also provide meaningful reference for other enterprises to carry out compensation system reform and promote common prosperity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《薪酬管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薪酬体系选择的影响因素；薪酬设计的原则；全面薪酬的内涵和具体要素；双因素理论；全面薪酬的公平性；公平理论；薪酬管理如何实现企业的高质量发展与员工的共同富裕</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
